动力系统提供电能，以延长续航里程的电动汽车，且该车载辅助供电装置与驱动系统没有传动轴（带）等传动连接。 简单地来说，增程式电动车是一种串联式插电混合动力汽车，其中的发动机不参与动力供应，其作用仅限于在动力系统需要时，用来带动发电机发电。背着燃油充电宝的电动车？增程式为何在争议声中销量狂飙 _10% 公司 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-88e5b93a6199e99d34aeeb3f27673b08_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626797416"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIza+jxKvqkpUpEAMaCTEwMTU2NzQ0NCC/n8KpBjAAOLUBQB1yCTYyNjc5NzQxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1697706492.161987", "card_id": "Q_616948265", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果隆美尔在东线会不会有更大的成就？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/616948265"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iza+jxKvqkpUpEAMaCDk5Mzc5ODI3IK3Z3KYGMAA4PUAecgk2MTY5NDgyNjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1697706492.162315", "card_id": "Q_626805114", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 115}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些既健康又省电，性价比拉满的空调值得推荐？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "随着科技与健康意识的共同进步，空调已经从单纯的温度调节工具，逐步转变为健康生活的重要组成部分。在现代家庭中，选择一款既能为我们带来舒适温度，又能确保健康空气质量，同时又具有低能耗的空调变得尤为关键。市场上到底有哪些空调既健康又省电，且性价比极高呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/81cc31cae_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626805114"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIza+jxKvqkpUpEAMaCTEwMTU2OTEyMCDhusKpBj